        <defName>HP_Adamantium</defName>
        <label>Adamantium</label>
        <description>Adamantium in the Warhammer 40,000 universe is an exceptionally durable and rare metal alloy, known for its incredible strength and resilience. Forged through arcane and complex processes, this material is a cornerstone in the construction of Imperial armor and structures. Its legendary toughness and ability to withstand extreme conditions make it a symbol of unyielding defense in the grim and war-torn 41st millennium.</description>
